_sText:
A deathrun map set in space.
Fixes / Changes:
No lame trailed grenades (but still the jetpacks & stuff)
Code area is now harder to get into
Glitchers are now killed instead of just stopped
Better texturing (Custom Textures!)

-40 Ct spawns
-3 T spawns
-20 traps - not including touch-breaks
-3 hidden, secret areas, one with a code!
-original ideas and designs!

End areas pictured in screenshots 2, 3 and 4.
A hidden area pictured last

If you have played this map please leave feedback so i can improve this map in the future. Thanks a lot guys!

                          -T955i-
